rive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwiT_rrkt-uTAxVlr4oHHUf0JtZIhKGwnKvF3dyiAcoBBC4Foeg=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqazItNWZIRk5falBtTTFBdGhUNDE2NWgzQTNZZ3xBQ3Jtc0trMU53TFBHQjVCdzZ2aTA4SnV5dDNXbmE1emlXaFJrNURrODlWbHhJc3lDM3hsbUxDUk12eVJFSk45LUl1Wk5MdWpoWEtYWjJRZWpYcWYyQWdNaHZHeUZNcV9JckhLbHJGdlg4U1BvV2kzLTJjaUptNA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=orl2KrOMEIQ","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqazItNWZIRk5falBtTTFBdGhUNDE2NWgzQTNZZ3xBQ3Jtc0trMU53TFBHQjVCdzZ2aTA4SnV5dDNXbmE1emlXaFJrNURrODlWbHhJc3lDM3hsbUxDUk12eVJFSk45LUl1Wk5MdWpoWEtYWjJRZWpYcWYyQWdNaHZHeUZNcV9JckhLbHJGdlg4U1BvV2kzLTJjaUptNA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=orl2KrOMEIQ","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwiT_rrkt-uTAxVlr4oHHUf0JtZIhKGwnKvF3dyiAcoBBC4Foeg=","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa2x6bXN1QV90ODZ1WmdYVEN6RUs5Y1hnUzh5Z3xBQ3Jtc0ttNFNsbTdvRmUxVXN6Y29BTk9RVWNYZURMbE1pVFRWWE55N2x5ZWI1MmdHd1hRcEVrRnFIb251UTBmbmVIb3BGM2oxSU5oSThQZVRWMDZtSV9SUGlleFR6LTBwTF9tMmVzeVVyYWE5Y2FyY0hiWDRiWQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pay